Read T_LEVEL.out

Source: R/read_tlevel.R
read_tlevel.Rd

Read T_LEVEL.out

Usage

read_tlevel(path)

Arguments

path

full path to T_LEVEL.out file

Value

imports T_LEVEL out with tidy column names and saves metainformation in attribute 'meta'

Examples

path_tlevel <- system.file("extdata/model/test/T_LEVEL.out", package = "kwb.hydrus1d")
tlevel <- read_tlevel(path = path_tlevel)
